OL,3,GNEWSCBBC Politics Live launches new
OL,4,Clook graphics and studio
OL,5,
OL,6,FAs before, there's a large LED wall at
OL,7,Fthe back of the set but with new
OL,8,Fvisuals, including a stylised London
OL,9,Fskyline and the circle elements from
OL,10,Fthe programme's new title sequence.
OL,12,FThe digital background imagery also
OL,13,Fincludes faux glass and wooden panels.
OL,15,FOn-screen graphics have been
OL,16,Foverhauled, with a more modern look and
OL,17,Ffeel, with a means of accommodating
OL,18,Fviewer contributions throughout the
OL,19,Fprogramme, mostly in the form of text.
