OL,3,GNEWSCBBC Politics Live launches new
OL,4,Clook graphics and studio
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe new titles make use of the new
OL,7,Fin-house Atlas design system, which
OL,8,Ffeatures elements that are a
OL,9,Fsimplification of the main BBC News
OL,10,FGlobe ` in this case, red/pink/orange
OL,11,Fcircles, mixed with stock imagery of
OL,12,Fpeople at work.
OL,14,FThose involved in the relaunch of the
OL,15,Fprogramme: Erron Gordon, Chris Cook,
OL,16,Fdirector Janet McAllen, project manager
OL,17,FAdam Stansill and graphic design team
OL,18,Flead Sue Vago.
OL,20,FSet design was by Sarah Milton. Music
OL,21,Fwas developed by Sitting Duck Music.
